node.text:
Do you remember all those little diecast West Coast Choppers bikes I used to sell at Wal*Mart?? 
Well my partner in that business, “Fred”. Is my partner in our Ammo business : Ammo Inc. 
Exciting times for this venture!
Not only did we just purchase Gunbroker.com. We also own Jagemann Brass in Manitowoc Wisconsin. That’s right down the road from out New Ammo Inc Facilities. I don’t usually toot my horn much on business stuff, but this one is pretty Damn cool! 

If you dig this stuff please follow these...
@ammoincusa 
@jessejamesammo 
@gunbroker 

Also if you’re interested in stock.
We are “POWW” on Nasdaq👍🏽

Thank you!🙏🏻🙏🏻

#jessejames

This JJFU “Cisco” 1911 definitely ticks all the boxes.

✔️Perlage finish JJFU TearDropped Bushing Barrel chambered in 10mm

✔️Deep Relief Engraved Slide with 24k gold inlay, JJFU Electric Blue finish.

✔️Deep relief engraved grips with 24k gold inlay, hand polished.

✔️Stainless Steel frame with Perlage finish flats with matte finish grip surface.

✔️JJFU Fang trigger & Trap hammer.

✔️JJFU 10mm magazine witb Perlage finish and Electric Blue base plate.

✔️Boxed up in a in-house handmade Mississippi Black Walnut presents box.

☑️All Proudly Made in Austin Texas USA🇺🇸
